<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@500;700;800&display=swap');
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
  html,body{width:1200px;height:630px;overflow:hidden;}
  body{
    font-family:'Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro','Noto Sans JP','Yu Gothic',system-ui,sans-serif;
    background:#FFFFFF;
    position:relative;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
  }
  .icon-row{display:flex;gap:14px;margin-bottom:36px;}
  .icon-row .dot{width:14px;height:14px;border-radius:50%;background:#EAF0E2;border:2px solid #C9C9C1;}
  .icon-row .dot:nth-child(1){border-color:#C9C9C1;}
  .icon-row .dot:nth-child(2){border-color:#BFBFB5;}
  .icon-row .dot:nth-child(3){border-color:#A9C79A;}
  .icon-row .dot:nth-child(4){border-color:#8FBE79;background:#EAF0E2;}
  .icon-row .dot:nth-child(5){border-color:#7C9169;background:#EAF0E2;}
  .headline{
    font-size:56px;
    font-weight:800;
    color:#1A1A1A;
    text-align:center;
    line-height:1.45;
  }
  .pill{
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:10px;
    background:#EAF0E2;
    color:#3F4F38;
    padding:4px 26px;
    border-radius:999px;
  }
  .pill-dot{width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:50%;background:#7C9169;display:inline-block;}
  .sub{
    margin-top:28px;
    font-size:22px;
    font-weight:500;
    color:#666666;
  }
  .byline{
    margin-top:44px;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:14px;
    font-size:18px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:#1A1A1A;
  }
  .byline .sep{color:#C9C9C1;font-weight:400;}
  .byline .role{font-weight:500;color:#666666;font-size:16px;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="icon-row">
    <span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span>
  </div>
  <p class="headline">小さなストレスが、<br><span class="pill"><span class="pill-dot"></span>仕組み</span>に変わる。</p>
  <p class="sub">PDF・AI・伝達のつまずきから、売上導線まで。</p>
  <div class="byline">
    <span>窪田成功</span><span class="sep">|</span><span class="role">感覚を仕組みにする参謀</span>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
